Context:
Owen Buckley and Ryan Sutherland won gold and silver respectively at the HRAI Heating System Technician Competition held on March 24, 2023, at the Canadian Mechanical and Plumbing Exposition at the Metro Convention Centre. They are students in the Heating, Refrigeration and Air Conditioning program at George Brown College. Professor Steven Racey commended their impressive performances. Brandon Sisco also participated in the competition. Haris Rahmati, who trained with Owen, Ryan, and Brandon, was unable to attend.
